===Etymology===

From Proto-Athabascan *''-x̯ɑ̓t’''. 

Cognates: Western Apache ''[[sig#Western Apache|sig]] ~ shig ~ [[sid#Western Apache|sid]] ~ [[shid#Western Apache|shid]]'', Mescalero ''sįh''.

===Noun===
'''sid''', '''-zid''' ''possessed form'' (e.g., '''shizid''' "my scar", '''bizid''' "her/his/their scar")

#[[scar]]

